<th align="center" bgcolor="lightblue" colspan="3"><big>Economy of<br />
the People's Republic of China</big></th>
</tr>
<tr>
<th align="left" valign="top"><a href="/wiki/Currency" title="Currency">Currency</a></th>
<td colspan="2" valign="top"><a href="/wiki/Chinese_yuan" title="Chinese yuan">yuan</a> (CNY); also referred to as the <a href="/wiki/Renminbi" title="Renminbi">Renminbi</a> (RMB)</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<th align="left" valign="top"><a href="/wiki/Exchange_rate" title="Exchange rate">Exchange rate</a> (<a href="/wiki/Fixed_exchange_rate" title="Fixed exchange rate">Manipulated by state</a>) (2007)</th>
<td colspan="2" valign="top">Rmb:<a href="/wiki/United_States_dollar" title="United States dollar">$ USD</a> = 6.87<br />
Rmb:<a href="/wiki/Japanese_yen" title="Japanese yen">¥ JPY</a>100 = 6.47<br />
Rmb:<a href="/wiki/Euro" title="Euro">€ EUR</a> = 10.55<br />
Rmb:<a href="/wiki/Pound_sterling" title="Pound sterling">£ GBP</a> = 15.23</td>
</tr>
